<BR><BR>EXAMPLE 7
<BR><BR>Example 4 is repeated except that the initial ingredients and their amounts are replaced with: 150 Gm amoxycillin, 75 Gm ranitidine, 1.50 Gm magnesium stearate, and 73.5 Gm hydroxypropylcellulose.  The final dosage form thus fabricated will
deliver 100 mg of amoxicillin and 50 mg of ranitidine over a time period of from 4 to 8 hours.
